Package: PKI
Version: 0.1-2
Title: Public Key Infrastucture for R based on the X.509 standard
Author: Simon Urbanek <Simon.Urbanek@r-project.org>
Maintainer: Simon Urbanek <Simon.Urbanek@r-project.org>
Depends: R (>= 2.9.0), base64enc
Enhances: gmp
Description: This package provides PKI functions such as verifying certificates, RSA encription and signing which can be used to build PKI infrastructure and perform cryptographic tasks.
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3 | file LICENSE
URL: http://www.rforge.net/PKI
SystemRequirements: OpenSSL library
